snippet.title: World's Worst Handyman - Future Games Show: Summer Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Wishlist Worlds Worst Handyman on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1333930/Worlds_Worst_Handyman/

Suit up as the "World's Worst Handyman" in this comedy stealth game where every job is a chaotic adventure! Dodge disgruntled clients, bungle repairs, and save your beloved animal shelter from bankruptcy.


https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #worldsworsthandyman
